3D/AR/VR App

The portal will be built with the 3D/AR/VR App from https://github.com/echo3Dco. 
There will be a unique portal for each faction in the portal.
You can buy land packages in the portal.
The avatar matrix and nft's you own will be incorporated in the land package metaverse.
There may also be a staking feature where you stake spacial (monoTomic Gold NFT's) to earn.
There are many more features we intend to bring as the game progresses to enhance the use gaming experience.
